{
  "id": "69b086705f16aedaae71e479",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:評価懸念",
  "created": 1773176480,
  "updated": 1773176501,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b086705f16aedaae71e479",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:評価懸念",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176480,
      "updated": 1773176480
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a0000000000047da4c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176480,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da4d",
      "text": "「はいはーい！今日のゆるトーク会、始まりました〜。テーマは[** “評価懸念”！]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da4e",
      "text": "かんたんに言うとさ、[** “周りの人にどう思われるか気になりすぎて動けなくなるやつ”]って感じ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da4f",
      "text": "テストとかSNSとか、めっちゃあるくない？ “いいね少なっ…詰んだw”みたいなやつ。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da50",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da51",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da52",
      "text": "「ええ……ございますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da53",
      "text": "人のまなざしというものは、ときに春風のようにやさしく、ときに冬の風のように胸に冷たく触れますもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da54",
      "text": "たとえば授業で手を挙げるときなども、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da55",
      "text": "『もし間違えていたら、どう思われるかしら』と、心がそっとためらうことがあります。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da56",
      "text": "それは決して弱さではなくて……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da57",
      "text": "人と人とが共に生きる中で、自然に芽生える感情なのだと思います。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da59",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da5a",
      "text": "「概念を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da5b",
      "text": "[** 評価懸念（evaluation apprehension）]とは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da5c",
      "text": "“他者から評価される状況で、失敗や否定を恐れて行動が抑制される心理”を指す。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da5d",
      "text": "心理学では古くから研究されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da5e",
      "text": "社会的促進理論とも関係がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da5f",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da60",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evaluation_apprehension",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da61",
      "text": "要点だけ言うと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da62",
      "text": "[** “人が見ているとパフォーマンスが変わる”]という現象の原因の一つ。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da63",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da64",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da65",
      "text": "「おおー、りかのいつもの理系まとめモードきた。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da66",
      "text": "でもさ、それって部活でもあるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da67",
      "text": "練習だとできるのに、試合だとミスるやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da68",
      "text": "あれってつまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da69",
      "text": "“みんな見てる→やば→手が震える”",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da6a",
      "text": "っていうメンタルデバフってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da6c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da6d",
      "text": "「概ね正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da6e",
      "text": "ただし完全な“デバフ”とも言えない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da6f",
      "text": "観客や評価者の存在は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da70",
      "text": " 簡単な作業 → 成績が上がる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da71",
      "text": " 難しい作業 → 成績が下がる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da72",
      "text": "という傾向がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da73",
      "text": "これを[** 社会的促進（social facilitation）]という。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da74",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da75",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_facilitation",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da76",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da77",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da78",
      "text": "「まあ……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da79",
      "text": "人の気配が、力を引き出すこともあるのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da7a",
      "text": "舞台に立つ役者が、観客の息づかいを感じて、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da7b",
      "text": "普段よりもいっそう輝く……そのようなことに似ているのでしょうか。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da7c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da7d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da7e",
      "text": "「比喩として適切。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da7f",
      "text": "ただし複雑な思考を要する場面では逆効果になりやすい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da80",
      "text": "テストやプレゼンなどが典型例。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da82",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da83",
      "text": "「なるほどねー。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da84",
      "text": "だからさ、クラスで[** “当てられたくないマン”]が大量発生するのか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da85",
      "text": "先生『じゃあ次、ふーこさん』",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da86",
      "text": "ふーこ『あ、回線落ちました』",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da87",
      "text": "…みたいな。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da89",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da8a",
      "text": "（笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da8b",
      "text": "「ふーこさん、それは回線ではなく心が落ちておりますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da8c",
      "text": "けれど、わたくしも似たようなものです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da8d",
      "text": "答えが分かっていても、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da8e",
      "text": "『間違えて誰かを困らせたらどうしましょう』と思ってしまうことがございます。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da8f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da90",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da91",
      "text": "「興味深い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da92",
      "text": "評価懸念は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da93",
      "text": "[* 能力が低いから起きるわけではない。]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da94",
      "text": "むしろ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da95",
      "text": " 真面目",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da96",
      "text": " 他者への配慮が強い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da97",
      "text": " 完璧主義",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da98",
      "text": "こういう人ほど強くなる傾向がある。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da99",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da9a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da9b",
      "text": "「え、じゃあ、あやって典型タイプじゃん。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da9d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da9e",
      "text": "「そう言われますと、少し照れてしまいますね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047da9f",
      "text": "けれど……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa0",
      "text": "人の気持ちを思うこと自体は、悪いことではありませんよね。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa2",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa3",
      "text": "「同意する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa4",
      "text": "問題は[** “評価を気にすること”ではなく“評価が行動を止めてしまうこと”]。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa5",
      "text": "対処法はいくつかある。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa8",
      "text": "「お、攻略法きた！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daa9",
      "text": "ゲームならここでチュートリアル入るやつ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daaa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daab",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daac",
      "text": "「簡潔に三つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daad",
      "text": " 1. 評価ではなくタスクに集中する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daae",
      "text": "  “どう思われるか”ではなく",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daaf",
      "text": "  “何をするか”に注意を向ける。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab0",
      "text": " 2. 小さい成功体験を増やす",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab1",
      "text": "  安全な環境で発言や挑戦を繰り返す。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab2",
      "text": " 3. 評価環境を変える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab3",
      "text": "  心理的安全性の高い集団にいる。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab4",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab5",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychological_safety",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab7",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab8",
      "text": "「心理的安全性……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dab9",
      "text": "それは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daba",
      "text": "“間違えても責められない場所”",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dabb",
      "text": "というような意味でしょうか。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dabc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dabd",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dabe",
      "text": "「その理解で正しい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dabf",
      "text": "Googleの研究でも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac0",
      "text": "チームの成果を決める最大要因の一つとされている。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac3",
      "text": "「つまりさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac4",
      "text": "“ミスっても笑われない空気のチームが最強”",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac5",
      "text": "ってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac8",
      "text": "「かなり近い。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dac9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daca",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dacb",
      "text": "「それは、素敵ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dacc",
      "text": "人が安心して声を出せる場所というのは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dacd",
      "text": "まるで静かな図書館のように、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dace",
      "text": "思考がやさしく広がる気がいたします。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dacf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad1",
      "text": "「いいねそれ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad2",
      "text": "じゃあさ、まとめるよー！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad4",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad5",
      "text": "「要点整理を補助する。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad8",
      "text": "「よし。今日の結論！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dad9",
      "text": " 評価懸念＝人にどう思われるか気になりすぎる現象",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dada",
      "text": " 見られてると簡単なことは強くなるけど、難しいことはミスりやすい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dadb",
      "text": " 解決のカギは安心できる環境",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dadc",
      "text": "って感じ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dadd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dade",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dadf",
      "text": "「概ね正確。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae1",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae2",
      "text": "「ええ、とても分かりやすいまとめです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae3",
      "text": "人の視線は、ときに重く感じられますけれど……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae4",
      "text": "やさしいまなざしの中では、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae5",
      "text": "人はのびのびと花を咲かせるのでしょうね。（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae8",
      "text": "「おお〜詩っぽい締めきた。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047dae9",
      "text": "じゃ、今日はこのへんで！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daea",
      "text": "次のテーマどうする？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daeb",
      "text": "[** “SNS承認欲求”]とか、めちゃ相性よさそうじゃない？w」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daed",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daee",
      "text": "「関連テーマとして妥当。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daef",
      "text": "議論の連続性もある。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daf0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daf1",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daf2",
      "text": "「それはまた、興味深いお話になりそうですね。」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a1000000000047daf3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176482,
      "updated": 1773176482
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a4000000000047daf4",
      "text": "#2026-03-11",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176484,
      "updated": 1773176501
    },
    {
      "id": "69b086a6000000000047daf5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176487,
      "updated": 1773176487
    }
  ]
}